h enraging blow isnt required for keeping agro.  In fact, the very idea of relying on a proc to gain agro is quite unsettling to me, I would rather rely on myself, not the luck of the draw.  I consider procs a bonus to a weapon, not a necessity. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=193009"> Grendon's Stuff </a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
